@using BForms.Docs.Helpers
<h3 id="Input-Email">Email Input</h3>

<p>        
    In order to render a text input of type email you will need to use the 
    <code>@@Html.BsInputFor</code> helper extension and 
    decorate your model property with <code>[BsControl(BsControlType.Email)]</code>.
    Using <code>BsControlType.Email</code> will enforce email validation on both client and server side.
</p>

